<view class="page">
  <view class="background-glow glow-top"></view>
  <view class="background-glow glow-bottom"></view>

  <view class="top-bar">
    <view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack">‹</view>
    <view class="top-title">第一个探索任务</view>
    <view class="top-placeholder"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="mission-header">
    <view class="mission-label">任务 01</view>
    <view class="mission-title">寻找搬运大师</view>
  </view>

  <view class="mission-card">
    <view class="character-area">
      <view class="character-glow"></view>
      <view class="ant">🐜</view>
      <view class="leaf-platform"></view>
    </view>

    <view class="character-name">蚂蚁</view>

    <view class="dialogue">
      “我忘记了自己的名字，<br />
      请帮我找回记忆。”
    </view>

    <view class="mission-description">
      找到一只蚂蚁，拍下清晰照片。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="clue-card">
    <view class="clue-title">探索线索</view>

    <view class="clue-row">
      <view class="clue-tag">花坛边</view>
      <view class="clue-tag">树根旁</view>
      <view class="clue-tag">石缝里</view>
    </view>

    <view class="safety-tip">
      不要触碰或伤害它
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="action-area">
    <view class="start-button" bindtap="beginMission">
      拿起镜头，开始寻找
    </view>

    <view class="safety-hint">
      探索时请让家长陪在身边
    </view>
  </view>
</view>